Poskrbite, da ne odobrite preveč splošnih ali sumljivih spletnih naslovov, ki ne prihajajo iz affiliata.

Upravljajte vse vaše pasice in povezave tukaj. Ustvarite lahko različne vrste oglasov: slike, besedile povezave, PDF, Flash, HTML pasice ali promocijska e-poštna sporočila. Vsakemu oglasu mora pripadati določena akcija (opredelitev provizije za napotitev) in ciljni URL.

Ta prvi korak je zelo pomemben
. Moral bi imeti načrt, kaj želite doseči. Kako velike provizije si lahko privoščitei?
Bo privlačna za affiliate, v primerjavi z vašo konkurenco? Kako privabiti nove affiliate k vpisu?

Post Affiliate Pro je narejen tako, da lahko deluje s privzeto konfiguracijo.
Vseeno pa bi morali preveriti konfiguracijo in jo prilagoditi za svoje lastne potrebe. podroben opis vseh možnosti konfiguracije lahko najdete v priročniku za uporabo ali bazi znanja.

En privzeta akcija se ustvari med namestitvijo. Lahko jo spremenite ali pa ustvarite svoje akcije.

Akcije se uporabljajo za nabor izdelkov (ali samo en proizvod), ki imajo nastavljene enake provizijee.

Na primer, lahko imate akcijo za Product1, kjer boste nagradili svoje affiliate na klik in drugo oglaševalsko akcijo za Product2, kjer affiliate prejme provizije za prodajo.

Ali pa ustvarite akcijo nizko cenovnih proizvodov, ki bodo imeli 40% prodajne provizije, in drugo akcijo dragih izdelkov z 15% prodajno provizijo.

Ali potrebujete pomoč pri konfiguraciji strukture provizij? "

V upravitelju transnadrejenii , ki jih različne oglase, iz besedilne povezave, standardnih pasic slike v HTML, Flash in transnadrejenii promocijskih email. Lahko
Vsak oglas mora imeti ciljni URL določeno - to je naslov, kjer se obiskovalec preusmerjen po kliku

Ali potrebujete pomoč pri razvoju napise? "

Morali bi vzpostaviti emailing funkcije. To vključuje:
  • poštni račun - kako se pošiljajo e-poštna sporočila. Izbirate lahko med mail () funkcijo ali SMTP strežnika
  • email predloge -. To so predloge, ki se uporabljajo, ko sistem samodejno pošlje e-pošto, kot po vpisu ali po prodajnih obvestil
  • e-obvestila -. lahko nastavite, kakšne obvestil želite prejemati kot trgovec, in kaj obvestila bodo na voljo za affiliate
Poskrbite, da poštni račun pravilno nastavljen - poskusite preizkusite pošiljanje e-pošte. Brez dela e-pošte so povezana affiliate ne bodo prejeli potrdilo o njihovih prijav, itd.

Preverite standardni prijavni obrazec in ga po potrebi prilagodite.

Obrazec za prijavo prihaja z mini spletne strani, ki vsebuje informacije o affiliate programu, itd
lahko uporabite mini spletno stran, ali pa jo izbrišete in uporabiti le prijavni obrazec.

Ali potrebujete pomoč pri oblikovanju dizajna? "

Affiliate plošča je zelo prilagodljiva.
Lahko, definirate kako bo izgledal meni, vsebina, ki jo želite imeti tam in celo napišete svoje vsebine ali povezavo do druge strani.

Ali potrebujete pomoč pri oblikovanju dizajna?

source:
Integration is a way to connect the affiliate system to your current website, shopping cart or payment gateway in a way that affiliate system will be notified about referrals and purchases.
When notified, affiliate system registers the sale, finds referring affiliate (if any) and creates appropriate commission for him.

Integration usually means adding few lines of code into your pages, and it is described step-by-step in the Integration guide for most common shopping carts and payment systems.%s
translation:
Integracija je način za povezovanje affiliate sistema z vašo spletno stranjo, nakupovalnim vozičkom ali plačilnim prehodom na način, da bo sistem beležil sistem napotitev in nakupov.
Ko affiliate sistem zazna prodajo, ugotavlja kdo je affiliata napotil (če sploh) in ustvari primerno provizijo za njega.

Integracija ponavadi pomeni dodati nekaj vrstic kode v vašo stran, kar je opisano v priročniku za integracijo z večino nakupovalnih vozičkov in plačilnimi sistemi.%s

Ko ste uspešno preizkusili integracijo affiliate sistema z vašo spletno stranjo, je vse pripravljeno za zagon vašega programa tako, da boste pritegnili k vpisu nove affiliate uporabnike.

Na vaši strani je nujno potrebo dodati povezavo do affiliate programa in/ali obrazca za prijavo. Imenujte povezavo npr; "Webmojstri bi radi zaslužili denar?" itd. To bo pritegnilo obiskovalce vaše spletne strani, ki jih lahko pretvorite v svoje affiliate uporabnike.

Da bi dosegli več potencialnih affiliatov vpišite svoj ??program na affiliate imenike. Obstaja minimalno deset imenikov na spletu, ki jih obiskuje več tisoč izkušenih affiliate uporabnikov vsak dan.

Welcome to our affiliate program

Use the menu to navigate through your panel.

source:
Hello and welcome to our affiliate program.
I'm your affiliate manager, and I'm here for you if you have ANY questions or problems related to our affiliate program.

I wish you all success in promoting our products, and profitable partnership for both you and us.
translation:
Pozdravljeni in dobrodošli v naš affiliate program.
Sem vaš affiliate manager in sem tukaj za vas, če imate kakršnakoli vprašanja ali težave, povezane z našim affiliate programom.

Želim vam veliko uspeha pri promociji naših izdelkov in storitev ter donosno affiliate partnerstvo za vas in za nas.

source: Are you sure you want to delete selected language(s)?

source: Campaign for commissions can be choosen by Product ID instead of banner. To do this you need to specify all product IDs that belong to this campaign. Product IDs need to be comma separated.
translation: Kampanja za provizije se lahko izbere po ID-ju izdelka namesto oglasa. Da bi to naredili morate določiti ID izdelkov, ki pripadajo tej akciji. ID-ji izdeleka morajo biti ločeni z vejico.

source: Type in unique Mailing list name

User will be redirected to this url in case he will confirm his registration in Mailing list. It is used in case Double Optin mechanism is used. If not defined, default message is displayed without redirection.
translation: Uporabnik bo preusmerjen na ta URL v primeru, da potrditi svojo registracijo na listo. Uporablja se v primeru, da se uporabiOptIn mehanizem. Če ni določen, privzeto prikaže sporočilo, brez preusmeritve.

source: Subscription to mailing list has to be confirmed by user. This is usually done by responding to a confirmation email sent to the email address in subsription request. This eliminates the chance of abuse where somebody submits somebody else's email address without their knowledge and against their will.
translation: Naročnina na poštni seznam mora biti potrjene s strani uporabnika. To se običajno izvede z odgovorom na potrditveno e-poštno sporočilo poslano na elektronski naslov, na zahtevo subsription. To odpravlja možnost zlorab, ko nekdo vloži nekdo drug e-poštni naslov brez njihove vednosti in proti njihovi volji.

source: Here you can find list of your Mailing Lists. You can manage listings by editing existing or adding new Newsletter.
translation: Tukaj lahko najdete seznam vaših glasil. Lahko upravljate sezname z urejanjem obstoječih ali dodajanjem novih.

source: For changes to take effect restart of application is needed. Do you want to restart now?
translation: Za potrebne spremembe znova zaženite aplikacijo. Zaženi zdaj?

source: You can contact us directly using this contact form. Your message will be sent to your affiliate manager by email.
translation: Lahko nas kontaktirate direktno, z uporabo tega kontaktnega obrazca. Vaše sporočilo bo poslano vašemu affiliate upravljalcu po elektronski pošti.

source: Please wait, import of selected languages can take few minutes.
translation: Počakajte, uvoz izbranih jezikov lahko traja nekaj minut.

source: Performance rewards is a powerful feature that allows you to reward your affiliates for their performance.
translation: Nagrada uspešnosti je močna funkcija, ki vam omogoča, da se nagradi affiliate za njihovo uspešnost.

source: Select your preferred theme for your affiliate panel.
translation: Izberite želeno temo za vašo affiliate ploščo.

source: With performance reward rule you can reward your affiliates for their performace and motivate them to refer more customers to you.
translation: Z nagrado za uspešnost lahko nagradite svoje affiliate za njihov nastop in jih motivirate, da k vam napotijo več kupcev.

source: To change translation just click on translation column. After you will change translation text, click button Save modified rows below table
translation: Če želite spremeniti prevod le kliknite na stolpec prevodov. Ko boste spremenili prevod besedila, kliknite gumb Shrani spremenjene vrstice pod tabelo

source:
If you want your campaign to have a special logo, specify it here.
Logo will be visible to your affiliates.
translation:
Če želite, da vaša akcija imeti poseben logotip, ga določite tukaj.
Logotip bo viden vaš affiliateh.

source:
Lifetime of cookie in days for this campaign. 0 means infinite. It defines for how many from the original referral your affiliate will get commissions.
For example, if you specify 14 days, affiliate will get commissions for all sales coming for the 14 days since visitor last click on his link.
translation:
Življenjska doba piškotkov v dnevih za to akcijo. 0 pomeni neskončno. Določa dodeliti število dni, ko affiliate dobi provizijo za napotitev.
Na primer, če navedete 14 dni, bodo affiliati dobili provizijo za vse prodaje, ki prihajajo v 14 dneh od dne ko je obiskovalec zadnjič kliknil na njegovo povezavo.

source: Request id is missing or unsupported
translation: Id zahteve pogrešan ali ni podprt

source: When advertising your affiliate links, you can track them using channels.
translation: Pri oglaševanju vaših affiliate povezav, jih lahko spremljate z uporabo kanala.

source: To use it, simply create a new channel for every link placement you want. In banners you can choose to get the link version with channel appended.
translation: Če ga želite uporabiti, ustvarite nov kanal za vsako povezavo, ki jo želite. V oglasu lahko izberete priložen kanal.

source: The channel parameter will be transferred also to the tracked commission, so you will know exactly what link led to the commission.
translation: Kanal parametrov se bo prenesel tudi na sledljivost provizije, tako da boste točno vedeli, katera od povezav je ustvarila provizijo.

source: PPC campaigns - you can have multiple ads for the same affiliate link. By using channel unique for every ad you can find out which ad converts more.
translation: PPC kampanje - lahko imate več oglasov za isto affiliate povezavo. Z edinstvenim kanalom za vsak oglas lahko ugotovite kateri oglas ustvarja več konverzije.

source: Links may not be changed. If you want to change link, you can delete the old link and create new, which must merchant again approve
translation: Povezave se ne sme spreminjati. Če želite spremeniti povezavo, lahko izbrišete stare povezave in ustvariti nove, ki jih mora trgovec spet odobriti

source: Here you can download export files for all payouts grouped by payout option.

translation: S klikom na predogled računa lahko vidite, kako bo izgledal račun za določenega affiliata.

source: You can specify name and format of mass pay export file for this payout option.
translation: Določite lahko ime in obliko množične datoteke za izplačilo.

source: When you pay your affiliates you will be able to download export file for each payout option.
translation: Ko boste plačali svoje affiliatom boste mogli prenesli izvozno datoteko za vsako izplačilno možnost.

source: Format of this file consists of three parts: header, row and footer template.
translation: Oblika tega dokumenta je sestavljena iz treh delov: glave, noge in vrstic predloge.

source: Header is at the beginning of the file, row is generated for each affiliate that is going to be paid and footer is at the end of file.
translation: Glava je na začetku datoteke, se vrstica, pripravljene za vsakega affiliata affiliate, ki se bo treba plačati, in noga je na koncu datoteke.

source: In each of this templates you can use Smarty syntax and row template allows you also to use some other constants.
translation: V vsakem od teh predlogh lahko uporabite Smarty sintakso in konstante za vrstico.

source: List of supported template constants is visible in the listbox above the row template text area.
translation: Seznam podprtih konstant predloge je viden v oknu s seznamom nad predloge vrstice besedila območju.

source: HTML format of the invoice for users with VAT applicable.
translation: HTML format računa za uporabnike, ki so DDV zavezanci.

source: You have to select affiliate for this preview
translation: Za ta predogled morate izbrai affiliata

source: You don't need to enter each and every URL address of your pages, you can use star convention.
translation: Ni vam treba vnesti vseh URL naslovov vaše strani, lahko uporabite zvezdico konvencije.

source: This video will help you better understand the Affiliate panel and quickly start promoting.
translation: Ta video vam bo pomagal bolje razumeti Affiliate ploščo in hitro začeti z promocijo.

source: In this video Chuck Lasker explains and clicks through basic forms of merchant control panel. He will show you how to navigate through main sections of application. In same time you can see in action how responsive is merchant application based on new Web 2.0 user interface.
translation: V tem videu Chuck Lasker pojasnjuje in klika po osnovnih oblikah nadzorne plošče trgovca. On vam bo pokazal, kako krmariti skozi glavna področja uporabe. V istem času boste lahko videli v akciji, kako odziven je nov 2,0 uporabniškiega vmesnik.

source: Custom value separator should be set only when custom value is used by other script. See Paypal (IPN and custom used by other script) integration method.
translation: Ločilnik vrednosti po meri samo, če vrednost po meri uporabljajo kakšna druga skripta. Oglejte si Paypal (IPN in druge skripte) integracijsko metodo.

source: When you check this option, recurring commissions won't be given automatically, but you wil have to trigger them using API. More details at: %s
translation: Ko izberete to možnost, ponavljajoče se provizije ne bodo avtomatično, sprožene, ampak se bodo sprožile z uporabp API-ja. Več podrobnosti na: %s

source: This step will check integrity of applications.
translation: Ta korak bo preveril integriteto aplikacij.

source: This step will update application files from distribution zip file located in install/ folder.
translation: Ta korak bo posodobitev daoteke iz distribucijske zip datoteke, ki se nahajajo v /install mapi.

source: To do this you need to specify correct ftp access info to your system. Because of permissions files are copied using ftp.
translation: Da bi to naredili morate določiti pravilno ftp info dostop do vašega sistema. Zaradi permissions datoteke se kopirajo uporabo ftp.

translation: Instalacija je bila prekinjena, ker je bila presežen čas izvedbe. Osvežite brskalnik, da se bo proces nadaljeval

source: Forced matrix allows you to limit to the number of referrals of subaffiliates any affiliate can refer. It means that every affiliate can have only specified number of children.
translation: Prisiljena matrika vam omogoča, da omejite število napotitev za podrejene. To pomeni, da ima lahko vsaka affiliate le določeno število podrejenih.

source: Read more details about Forced Matrix in our knowledgebase:
translation: Preberite več podrobnosti o Matrix v naši Knowledgebase:

source: Width of matrix - the number of subaffiliates allowed for every affiliate. 0 or empty field means unlimited. If you use example 3, every affiliate can have 3-9-27-81-... subaffiliates under them.
translation: Širina matrike - je dovoljeno število podrejenih za vsakega affiliata. 0 ali prazno polje pomeni neomejeno. Če uporabljate naprimer število 3, lahko ima vsak affiliate3-9-27-81 - ... podrejenih pod sabo.

source: Height of matrix - number of levels that will be filled before you send new affiliates to spillover affiliate set below. 0 or empty field means unlimited
translation: Višina matrike - število ravni, ki bodo izpolnili, preden pošljete nove affiliate v affiliatu spillover iz nadaljevanju. 0 ali prazno polje pomeni neomejeno

source: affiliate will be saved as child to his original referring affiliate, as if matrix is not active
translation: affiliate bo shranjen kot podrejeni (otrok) od njegovega prvotno napotenega affiliata, ker matrika ni aktivna

source: affiliate will be saved without parent affiliate (sponsor)
translation: affiliate bo shranjen brez nadrejenega (starša) affiliata (sponzorja)

source: affiliate will be sent as child to this affiliate.
translation: affiliate bo poslan kot podrejeni (otrok) temu affiliatu.
Ko se odobri / zavrne affiliata za akcijo

source: In uploaded document were found following variables:
translation: V prenešenem dokumentu so bile ugotovljene, naslednje spremenljivke:

translation: Lahko si ogledate rebranded PDF dokument - enak rezultat bo videl vaš affiliate. Spremenljivke, bodo nadomeščene z vrednotami povezane z izbranim polji v seznamu.

source: This plugin helps you to use action commission for signups. You need to have action commission feature activated! Create an action commission in a campaign and remember its code. After activation of this plugin, configure it and set the action commission code. You are also allowed to define campaign ID to apply action from campaign that is not set as default.
translation: Ta vtičnik vam pomaga, da uporabite akcijsko provizijo za prijavo. Imeti morate vključeno funkcijo akcijskih provizij! Ustvarite akcijsko provizije v kampanji in se spomnite svoje kode kampanje. Po aktiviranju tega dodatka, nastavite kodo kampanje. Prav tako lahko vpišete ID kampanje, ki ni določena kot privzeta.

source: Change affiliate manager info visible in affiliate panel
translation: Spremenite informacije affiliate Manager-ja, ki je vidn v Affiliate plošči

translation: Preberite več v naši zbirki znanja

source: Can not connect to FTP server.
translation: Ne morem se povezati na FTP strežnik.

source: Lifetime of cookie in days for this commission group. 0 means infinite.
translation: Življenjska doba piškotkov v dnevih za to skupino provizije. 0 pomeni neskončno.

source: Check if .htaccess is ok at this location
translation: Preverite, če je .htaccess ok na tej lokaciji

source: Replicated site is at default location
translation: Replicirana stran je na privzetem mestu

source: Replicated site is at custom location
translation: Replicirana stran je na specifični lokaciji

translation: V replicirani strani lahko uporabite lahko naslednje spremenljivke

source: When you choose custom location, replicated site can be placed on any url you want but it needs further setup.

source: Referral ID can contain only [a-zA-Z0-9_-] characters. %s given
translation: Napotiteveni ID lahko vsebuje samo [az, AZ, 0-9] znake. %s vnešen

Kodea za akcijsko provizijo bi morala biti niz brez presledkov in posebnih znakov, ki jih boste pozneje uporabili v skripti za sledenje, da boste določili, da je treba uporabiti to akcijo. Oznaka mora biti edinstvena znotraj ene oglaševalske akcije, tako da ne more imeti isto oznako v isti kampanji.
Določite lahko poljubno HTML kodo brez oznak, kot npr. body, head, html. Znotraj HTML kode lahko uporabite spremenljivke, opredeljene zgoraj v izbirnem polju.

source: Every Coupon has assigned its code. This setting defines format of this code. source: Daily report is sent every day with the statistics of the day traffic and sales.
translation: Dnevno poročilo se pošlje vsak dan s statistiko dnevnega prometa in prodaje.

source: Weekly report is sent every week with the statistics of the week's traffic and sales. It is sent on the day specified in "report sent on" and contains data from the previous complete week. The first day of week can be specified in "week starts at".
translation: Tedensko poročilo se pošlje vsak teden s statistiko prometa na teden in prodaje. Pošlje se na dan določen v "poročilo poslano na" in vsebuje podatke iz celotnega prejšnjega tedna. Prvi dan v tednu se lahko definira v "teden se začne ob".

source: Set day of week on which report is sent
translation: Nastavite dan v tednu, ko se pošlje poročilo

source: Monthly report is sent every month with the statistics of the month's traffic and sales. It is sent on a day specified in "report sent on" and contains data from previous month. e.g. If "report sent on" is set to 31 and month has only 30 days, then the report is sent on the last day of the month. It is recommended that you set "report sent on" to one of the first days of month, so that data in report is current.
translation: Mesečno poročilo se pošlje vsak mesec, s statističnimi podatki o prometu in prodaji. Posalno bo na dan, določen v "poročilo poslano na" in vsebuje podatke iz prejšnjega meseca. npr. Če je "poročilo poslano na" nastavljeno na 31-tega v mesecu in ima mesec le 30 dni, je poročilo poslano na zadnji dan v mesecu. Priporočljivo je, da nastavite "poročilo poslano na" na enega od prvih dni v mesecu, tako da so poročila podatkov redna.

source: Set day of month on which report is sent

source:
Banner rotator is a special type of banner that rotates other banners.
When affiliate inserts rotator to his page, the rotator displays banners that are assigned to the rotator, so the visitor will see another banner every time he visits the affiliates page.
More help in our Knowledge Base
translation:
Oglasni rotator je posebna vrsta oglasa, ki rotira druge oglase.
Ko affiliate vnese rotator na svojo stran, rotator prikaže oglase, ki so dodeljeni posameznemu rotatorju, tako da bo obiskovalec vsakič, ko obišče affiliate stran, videl drug oglas .
Več pomoč v naših zbirkah znanja

Več valut vam omogoča, da spremljate prodajo v več valutah.

Privzeto je, da so vse akcije v %s, javne, kar pomeni, da si jih lahko affiliate ogleda in jih začne promovirati. Funkcija privatne akcije pa omogoča ustvarjanje zasebnih akcij, ki so vidne le za izbrane affiliate.

source:

All the rebranding is made automatically in the background.
%s
translation:
To vam omogoča ustvariti posebno vrsto promocijskih materialov - Rebrandable e-knjige. Lahko ustvarite PDF e-knjigo le enkrat in jo prenesite v affiliate %s. Vsak affiliate bo samodejno dobil svojo blagovno znamko in izvod knjige, s svojim imenom, affiliate povezavo in besedilom, itd ni treba uporabljati Windows programa. Ves rebranding se izvede samodejno v ozadju.
%s

source: It is possible to use following values in ID: {9} - will be replaced by any character in range [0-9], {z} - will be replaced by any character in range [a-z], {Z} - will be replaced by any character in range [A-Z], {X} - will be replaced by any character in range [0-9a-zA-Z], all other characters will be copied to refid as you will specify in format. Example of good format is e.g. {ZZZ}-{XXXXX}-{999}
translation: Možno je, da uporabite naslednje vrednosti ID: 9 - bo nomeščeno z znakom v območju [0-9] {z} - bo nadomeščen z vsakim znakom v območju [az] {Z} - bo nadomščen z vsakim znakom v območju [AZ] {X} - bo nadomeščen z znakom v območju [0-9a-zA-Z], vsi ostali znaki bodo kopirani refid-ju, kot boste določili v formatu. source: Refid must be in format "%s". Example of good format is e.g. {ZZZ}-{XXXXX}-{999}
translation: RefId mora biti v obliki "%s". Oblika formata : {9} - bo nomeščeno z znakom v območju [0-9] {z} - bo nadomeščen z vsakim znakom v območju [az] {Z} - bo nadomščen z vsakim znakom v območju [AZ] {X} - bo nadomeščen z znakom v območju [0-9a-zA-Z], vsi ostali znaki bodo ostali nespremenjeni, kot boste določili v formatu. Primer dobrega formata je na primer {ZZZ}-{XXXXX}-{999}

source: Choose which fields you want to use to store data for your network accounts. source:
SubId tracking can be made using Channels. For additional tracking, you can append up to two custom parameters data1 and data2 to the link URL.
These parameters will be transferred also to the tracked commission, so you will know exactly what link led to the commission.
translation:
Podidentifikator sledenja se lahko izvede z uporabo kanalov . Za dodatno sledenje, lahko dodate 2 poljubna podatka Podatek1 in Podatek2 k URL povezavi.
Ti parametri se prenešeni tudi za sledenje provizije, zato boste točno vedeli, katera povezava je privedla do provizije.

source:
You should put this clicks tracking code into EVERY page that will be the target of affiliate links.
The best practice is to put it somewhere into the footer of your page.
If you use good website content management system, this should guarantee that the tracking code will be executed in every page.
translation:
To kodo za sledenje klikov bi morali vstaviti v VSAKO STRAN, ki bo cilj affiliate povezave.
Najboljša praksa je, da jo vstavite v nogo strani.
Če uporabljate dober CMS, bo to zagotovilo, da se bo koda za sledenje izvajala na vsaki strani.

source:
Cookie privacy policy influences if the tracking cookies will be blocked by browsers, so it si important to set it.
You should set at least Compact P3P policy. If you don't want to generate it for your site, use the following string: NOI NID ADMa DEVa PSAa OUR BUS ONL UNI COM STA OTC
translation:
Vpliv politike zasebnosti piškotka, vpliva na blokiranje brskalnikov, zato je pomembno, da si jo postavilte.
Morate nastaviti vsaj P3P kompaktno politiko zasebnosti. Če jo ne želite ustvariti za vašo spletno stran, uporabite naslednji niz: NOI NID ADMa DEVa PSAa OUR BUS ONL UNI COM STA OTC

source:
GeoIp plugin is based on free GeoIp database offered by MaxMind.
Plugin requires GeoIp binary database (filename GeoLiteCity.dat) saved in your plugin directory (server/plugins/GeoIp/).
You can downlaod latest version of GeoIp database from here: %s.
(Don't forget to extract downloaded file before copying to plugin directory)
Free GeoIp database has lower accuracy as paid version offered by MaxMind, but for most of installations it will be enough, because in most cases you are interested in country level information and City level is not so important.
If you want to have more accurate results of IP identification, you will need to buy GeoCity library from %s and replace file GeoLiteCity.dat in your plugin directory with one you received from MaxMind.
Accuracy of Free GeoIp database: Over 99.3%% on a country level and 76%% on a city level for the US within a 25 mile radius.
Accuracy of Paid GeoIp database: Over 99.8%% on a country level and 81%% on a city level for the US within a 25 mile radius.
translation:
GeoIp plugin is based on free GeoIp database offered by MaxMind.
Plugin requires GeoIp binary database (filename GeoLiteCity.dat) saved in your plugin directory (server/plugins/GeoIp/).
You can downlaod latest version of GeoIp database from here: %s.
(Don't forget to extract downloaded file before copying to plugin directory)
Free GeoIp database has lower accuracy as paid version offered by MaxMind, but for most of installations it will be enough, because in most cases you are interested in country level information and City level is not so important.
If you want to have more accurate results of IP identification, you will need to buy GeoCity library from %s and replace file GeoLiteCity.dat in your plugin directory with one you received from MaxMind.
Accuracy of Free GeoIp database: Over 99.3%% on a country level and 76%% on a city level for the US within a 25 mile radius.
Accuracy of Paid GeoIp database: Over 99.8%% on a country level and 81%% on a city level for the US within a 25 mile radius.

source: When this is checked, every pending affiliate will be approved after successful payment.
translation: Ko je to označeno bo vsak affiliate v čakanju, po uspešnem plačilu odobren.

source: Could not change read only fields
If you have huge amount of incoming impressions, GeoIp for impressions can cause slowdown of impression processor and delay during loading statistics.
translation: Če imate veliko količino vhodnih prikazov, lahko GeoIP za prikaze povzroči upočasnitev procesorja prikazov in nastane zamuda med prikazom statistike.

source: Insert contact on a given day at the follow-up cycle. Value of 0 means the beginning of the cycle. Lack of this param means that a contact will not be inserted into cycle.
translation: Vstavite kontakt na določen dan v nadaljnem ciklu. Vrednost 0 pomeni začetek cikla. Pomanjkanje tega parametra pomeni, da kontakt ne bo vstavljen v ciklu.

source: Campaign does not belong to any category
Send registration notification on every sale
translation: Pošlji obvestilo registracije ob vsaki prodaji

source: Automatically registered affiliate receive registration notification only when first sale is created and approved. If this checkbox is checked, registration email is sent on every approved sale while affiliate login to affiliate panel.
translation: Samodejno registriran affiliate prejme obvestilo o registraciji, le, če je njegova prva prodaja odobrena. Če je to polje označeno, bo affiliate avtomatično prejeli e-pošto za vsako registrirano prodajo, ko se bo prijavil v affiliate nadzorno ploščo.

source: This feature allows to use (non)affiliate email address as affiliate parameter in sale/click tracking code. If email is not registered, new affiliate will be created automatically and he get notification about registration when he reach first approved commission. Notifications about sales will be disabled for this affiliate while he first login into affiliate panel. For generating affiliate link or banner code for new affiliates you can use HTML forms in Configuration > Affiliate signup > Auto registering forms.
translation: Ta možnost omogoča uporabiti (ne-affilatov) elektonski naslov kot affiliate parameter v sledenju prodaje/klikov. Če e-pošta ni registrirana, bo avtomatično ustvarjen nov affiliate in bo obveščen o registraciji, ko doseže prvo odobreno provizijo. Obvestila o prodaji bodo onemogočena za tega affiliata, dokler se prvič ne prijavi v affiliate nadzorno ploščo. Za generiranje affiliate povezave ali oglasne kode za nove affiliate, lahko uporabite HTML obrazec v Nastavitev--> Affiliate vpis--> Avtomatični obrazec za registracijo.

source: Auto Registering Affiliates - Affiliate - First Sale / Lead
translation: Avtomatično registrirani affiliati - Affiliate - Prva Prodaja

source: Welcome to our affiliate program - First Sale / Lead
translation: Dobrodošli na naši affiliate program - Prva prodaja

source: The number of custom field that you are using for integration (1 or 2). In case you are already using both custom fields for another purposes, you have to use method with adding custom details to an existing field - you have to define the separator value as well. See PagosOnline integration method.
translation: Število poljubnih polj, ki jih uporabljate za integracijo (1 ali 2). V primeru, da že obe uporabljate za druge namene, boste morali uporabiti metodo z dodajanjem poljubnih podrobnosti na obstoječe polje - določiti boste morali  tudi ločilniik vrednosti. Oglejte si PagosOnline integracijsko metodo.

source: Custom value separator should be only set in case custom field is already used by another script. See PagosOnline integration method.
translation: Ločilnik vrednosti, je treba nastaviti le v primeru, da je to polje že uporablja druga skripta. Oglejte si PagosOnline integracijsko metodo.

source: You have to specify Custom field number!
translation: Morate navesti številko polja po meri!

source: This plugin handles PagosOnline IPN notifications (integration of Post Affiliate with PagosOnline)
translation: Ta vtičnik upravlja PagosOnline IPN obvestila (integracija Affiliate Post s PagosOnline)

translation: Polje po meri, ki ga uporabljate v integriranih povezav (glej Premium Web Cart opis integracije).

translation: Ko je to označeno, bo z vsakim novim dogodkom ustvarjen affiliata iz kreditenc, ki so bile nastavljene v Premium Web Cart obrazcuc.

source: Process all items in cart as one transaction (not per product).

translation: Ko je to označeno, bo vsak do affiliate odobren po uspešnem plačilu.

source: This plugin handles Premium Web Cart IPN notifications (integration of Post Affiliate with Premium Web Cart)
translation: Ta vtičnik upravlja Premium Web cart IPN obvestila (povezovanje Affiliate Post s Premium Web Cart)

source: (BETA!) Enter the full URL where do you want to resend received data from Recurly. This is used in case you are using third party application that uses push notifications too. E.g. membership handler.
translation: (BETA!) vnesite celoten URL kamor želite poslati prejete podatke iz Recurly. To se uporablja v primeru, da uporabljate kakšno tretjo skripto, ki uporablja postisk obvestil za npr članstvo.

source: This plugin handles Recurly push notifications (integration of Post Affiliate with Recurly). The plugin only works with the custom code defined in the integration methods list.
translation: Ta vtičnik upravlja Recurly Push obvestila (integracija Affiliate Post s Recurly). Vtičnik deluje samo s kodo po meri, opredeljene v seznamu integracije.

source: new sale / lead was registered for you by our affiliate program.
translation: Novi prodaja / svinec je bila registrirana za vas naš affiliate program.

source: You have been automatilcally pre-registered and you can login using the following link
translation: Bili ste registrirani avtomatično in se lahko prijavite z uporabo naslednje povezave

source: Please login and fill up your Personal and Payment Details
translation: Prosimo, prijavite se in izpolnite svoje osebne in podatke o plačilu

source: NOTE: You need to insert correct banner ID into line: $bannerid = "11110001"; instead of '11110001'.
translation: OPOMBA: morate vstaviti pravilni ID oglasa v vrstico: $bannerid = "11110001"; namesto of '11110001'.

source: If you cannot use PHP code on your HTML pages, you can use iframe codes. They are more simply, but you cannot customize CSS styles.
translation: Če ne morete uporabljati PHP kodo na vaši HTML strani, lahko uporabite Iframe kode. So bolj preproste, vendar ne morete prilagoditi CSS stilov.

source: NOTE: You need to insert correct banner ID into banner code form as url parameter bannerid instead of '11110001'.
translation: OPOMBA: Vstaviti morate pravilen ID oglasa v obrazec kode oglasa, kot je url parameter bannerid namesto '11110001'.

source: Get your iframe link/banner code form
Affiliate link and banner code forms
HTML/PHP codes below you can use for generating affiliate link or banner code for your new affiliates. Just copy & paste the code below to a HTML/PHP page.
translation: HTML / PHP kode pod vami lahko uporabite za ustvarjanje affiliate povezav ali kode oglasa za vape nove affiliate. Preprosto kopirajte in prilepite spodnjo kodo na HTML / PHP stran.

source: NOTE: First two parts are customizable, but contains PHP parts, so it have to be inserted into PHP page and you need to have enabled url fopen wrapper (allow_url_fopen = On) on your server.
translation: OPOMBA: Prva dva dela sta prilagodljiva, vendar vsebujejo del PHP-ja, zato je treba vstaviti v PHP stran in morate imeti omogočen ovoj url = fopen (allow_url_fopen On) na strežniku.

source: If you cannot use PHP code on your HTML pages, you can use iframe codes below.
translation: Če ne morete uporabljati PHP kode na vaše strani , lahko uporabite Iframe kode spodaj.

source: Are you sure you want to remove this commission type for this campaign? This action delete all settings for this commission type. You need to have deleted all transactions connected to this commission type.
translation: Ali ste prepričani, da želite odstraniti ta tip provizije za to akcijo? Ta akcija izbriše vse nastavitve za ta tip provizije. Izbrisati morate vse transakcije, povezane s to vrsto provizije.

source: If is checked, created default campaign for new account (via account signup form) will be private
translation: Če je označeno bo ustvarjena privzeta akcjia za nov račun zasebna (preko vpisnega obrazca)

source: This setting is valid for new accounts from signup form
translation: Ta nastavitev velja za nove račune iz vpisnega obrazca

source: Please input valid certificate generated using your account CSR request.
translation: Prosimo vnesite veljaven certifikat, generiran z zahtevo CSR računa.

source: Please input valid CA bundle attached to your certificate.
translation: Prosimo vnesite veljaven CA bundle pripet k vašemu certifikatu.

source: This will be your primary domain. It can be second-level domain like mydomain.com, or third-level domain like example.mydomain.com. Press check button if it is ready to be used with your account.
translation: This will be your primary domain. It should be only third-level domain like example.mydomain.com. Please do NOT use 2nd level domains like mydomain.com. Press check button if it is ready to be used with your account.

source: Select which type of secure access do you wnat to use or disable it completely. You can also choose to use your own certificate.
translation: Izberite, katero vrsto varnega dostopa želite uporabljati ali onemogočite to v celoti. Izberete lahko tudi uporabo svojega certifikata.

source: Here you can configure your custom certificate. click Setup to proceed.
translation: Tu lahko nastavite vaš specifičen certifikat. kliknite Nastavitev za nadaljevanje.

source: Here you can download your certificate signup request. Use it to generate your own certificate.
translation: Tukaj si lahko prenesete zahtevo za prijavni certifikat. Uporabite ga za ustvarjanje svojega certifikata.

source: This domain was assigned to your account by QualityUnit. You can use it to access your account, but you can not change it.
translation: Ta domena je bila dodeljeno vašemu računu s QualityUnit. Lahko ga uporabite za dostop do računa, vendar pa ga ne morete spremeniti.

source: You select Custom certificate option, but forgot to setup certificate.
translation: Izbrali ste možnost poljubnega certifikata, vendar ste pozabili nastaviti certifkat.

source: Domain name can not be empty!
translation: Ime domene ne sme biti prazno!

source: Please enter valid domain name without http:// or htpps:// or slashes
translation: Vnesite veljavno ime domene brez http:// ali https:// ali poševnice

source: Domain name is invalid. Please enter valid domain name.
translation: Domena je neveljavna. Vnesite veljaveno ime domene.

source: Domain configuration in progress. Please wait...
translation: Konfiguracija domene je v teku. Prosimo, počakajte ...

source: CA bundle can not be recognized.
No key entry was found for this account. Please genrate CSR first.
translation: Ni bilo najdenega ključa za ta račun. Prosimo prvo generirajte CSR..

source: Unable to check domain. check if it is valid second or third-level domain.
translation: Ni mogoče preveriti domeno. preverite, če je veljavna druga ali tretja raven domene.

source: Domain is not set properly. A record and CNAME record are pointing to the smae location. Delete A record and use CNAME record only!
translation: Domena ni nastavljena pravilno. Zapis CNAME in kaže na isto mesto. Zbrišite zapisa A in uporabite le CNAME!

source: Domain is not set properly. A record is pointing to the right location, but use CNAME instead!
translation: Domena ni nastavljena pravilno. Zapis A kaže na pravem mestu, vendar uporabite CNAME!

source: Domain is not set properly. NS or CNAME record are missing or not correct.
translation: Domena ni nastavljena pravilno. NS ali CNAME manjka ali ni pravilen.

source: Certificate and private key do not match.
translation: Certifikat in zasebni ključ se ne ujemata.

source: Unable to get domain info. Try again later.
translation: Ni mogoče, da bi dobili informacije domene. Poskusite še enkrat kasneje.

source: Selected target attribute can be used in banner html, by using variable %s in banner format.
translation: Izbrani ciljni atribut se lahko uporablja v html oglasu, s spremenljivko %s v obliki oglasa.

source: Notice that you should fill up number fields (e.g. Commission, TotalCost) with number values, otherwise if in email template is used number or currency formatter %s you can get warning message.
translation: Opozorilo, da bi morali vpisati števlike polj. (npr. provizija, skupni stroški) z vrednostjo številk. Drugače, če uporabljate v predlogi e-pošte številke ali valuto %s lahko dobite opozorilno sporočilo.

source: value of total cost in sales
value of total cost in action commissions
translation: Vrednost vseh stroškov v akcijskih provizijah

source: value of total cost in sales and recurring sales
translation: Vrednost vseh stroškov prodaje v ponavljajoči prodaji

source: Campaign Scheduler allows you to schedule rules for automatically configuring the campaign status. You can set statistics or time conditions when campaign will be active or inactive.
translation: Urnik akcije vam omogoča, da načtrujete pravila za samodejno konfiguracijo stanja akcije. Nastavite lahko statistiko ali časovne pogoje, kdaj bo akcija aktivna ali neaktivena.

source: require cron job which is not running now. Please set it up in Tools -> Integration -> Cron Job Integration
translation: zahtevajo cron opravilo, ki ne teče zdaj. Prosimo, da ga je ustanovil v Orodja -> Integracija -> Cron Job Integracija

source: Scheduling Rule saved, but used time is in past.
translation: Razporejanje člen shrani, vendar se uporablja, ko je v preteklosti.

source: Unknown rule (%s) - this rule will not be applied.
translation: Neznano pravilo (%s) - to pravilo ne bodo uporabljeno.

source: Connect your affiliate program with Google+. Help your affiliates to share your banners through Google+ with friends.
translation: Povežite affiliate program z Google+. Pomagajte svojim affiliatom, da delijo vaše oglase na Google+ s prijatelji.

source: Connect your affiliate program with LinkedIn. Help your affiliates to share your banners through LinkedIn.
translation: Povežite affiliate program z LinkedIn. Pomagajte svojim affiliatom, da delijo vaše oglase na LinkedIn s prijatelji.

source: If account balance is lower than this value, network account will get 'Account low prepaid credit' email.
translation: Če je stanje na računu nižje od te vrednosti, bo račun za omrežje dobil e-pošto "Račun nizek predplačajte kredit" .

source: Send low credit notification on every sale while ballance is low
translation: Pošlji nizko kreditno obvestilo o vsaki prodaji, medtem ko je nizko stanje

source: Network merchant receive low credit notification only once when ballane is lower than inserted value or after each sale while ballance is low.
translation: Trgovec mreže bo prejeli nizko kreditno obvestilo le enkrat, ko bo stanje nižje od vpisane vrednosti ali po vsaki prodaji z nizkim stanjem.

source: If account ballance is lower than this value, network account will be suspended.
translation: Če bo stanje na računu nižje od te vrednosti, bo račun omrežja onemogočen.

source: Network Account Prepaid feature enables prepaid mode. Network merchants will need to have positive accounting balance, otherwise their accounts will be suspended (higher payments for account than their commissions).
translation: Predplačilo za račun omrežja je funkcija, ki omogoča predplačniški način. Mrežni trgovci bodo morali imeti pozitivno računovodsko stanje, sicer bodo njihovi računi prekinjeni (višja plačila za račun kot njihove provizije).

source: Your account has low prepaid credit
translation: Vaš račun ima nizek predplačniški kredit

source: You does not have privilege to edit prepaid settings!
translation: Nimate privilegija, da uredite nastavitve predplačil!

source: Must be bigger then "Ip address validity" defined below.
translation: Mora biti večji od "veljavnosti IP naslova" opredeljenega spodaj

source: Unable to get file from ftp
translation: Ne morem dobiti datoteke iz ftp
Provizija po meri za prvo prodajo

source: Custom value of the first commission. Each commission have to be defined as a number or %number e.g. %10 means 10% commission, otherwise flat commission will be used.
translation: Poljubna vrednot prve provizije. Vsako provizijo je treba opredeliti kot številko ali %številka, npr. %10 pomeni 10% provizije, sicer bo uporabljena fiksna provizija.
Provizija po meri za drugo prodajo

source: Custom value of the second (recurring) commission. First recurring sale comes with the same order ID, so we can easily recognize it. You can set up to 5 different recurring values, that means each recurrent payment can have a different commission.
translation: Poljubna vrednost druge (ponavljajoče se) provizije. Prva ponavljajoča prodajo prihaja z enakim ID-jem naročila, tako da jo lahko zlahka prepoznamo. Nastavite lahko do 5 različnih ponavljajočih vrednosti, kar pomeni, da ima lahko vsako ponavljajoče se plačilo, različno provizijo.
Provizija po meri za tretjo prodajo

source: Zero means to stop processing any next recurrings. E.g. if you want to limit commission to 3 recurrences only, you have to define 3 levels and 4th and 5th set as zero - '0'.
translation: Nič pomeni ustaviti procesiranje naslednje ponovitve. Npr Če želite omejiti provizijo samo do 3 ponovitve, boste morali definirati 3 stopnje in 4. in 5. nastaviti kot nič - '0'.
Provizija po meri za četrto prodajo
Provizija po meri za peto prodajo

source: If you want some campaigns to be excluded from custom level commissions, just write down all campaigns IDs here, semicolon separated.
translation: Če želite nekaj akcij izključiti iz provizij po meri, samo vpišite vse ID-je akcij, ločene z podpičjem.

source: GetResponse360 users have unique URL and it will be provided to them by GetResponse Account Manager. If you are using common GetResponse (not GetResponse360) let this field empty.
translation: GetResponse360 uporabniki imajo edinstven URL, ki jim ga zagotovlja upravitelja računa Getresponse. Če uporabljate Getresponse (ne GetResponse360) pustite to polje prazno.

source: Can be found in this same section under the title of ‘XML Username’.
translation: Can be found in this same section under the title of ‘XML Username’.

source: Can be found in this same section under the title of ‘XML Token’.
translation: Can be found in this same section under the title of ‘XML Token’.

source: You can find in the ‘User Accounts -> Edit User’ section of Interspire Email Marketer under the ‘User Permissions’ tab. Make sure that you have ‘Enable the XML API’ checked and saved. The XML Path will look similar to the following: http://www.yourdomain.com/IEM/xml.php
translation: You can find in the ‘User Accounts -> Edit User’ section of Interspire Email Marketer under the ‘User Permissions’ tab. Make sure that you have ‘Enable the XML API’ checked and saved. The XML Path will look similar to the following: http://www.yourdomain.com/IEM/xml.php

source: Interspire Email Marketer plugin configuration saved
translation: Interspire Email tržnik vtičnik nastavitve shranjene

source: After signup of affiliate to Post Affiliate Pro, this plugin will register user also in Interspire Email Marketer service. Plugins requires you to enter XML Path, username and usertoken. Visit Interspire Email Marketer here at %s
translation: Po vpisu affiliatua v Affiliate Pro, bo ta vtičnik registriral uporabnika tudi v e-poštno storitev Interspire. Nastavitev zahteva vnos XML poti, uporabniško ime in usertoken. Obiščite Interspire Email tukaj %s

source: Save as unreferred (if set in tracking settings)
translation: Shranite kot nenapoten (če je nastavljeno nastavitvah sledenja)

source: Custom commission value for lifetime referrals - if the transaction is tracked for a lifetime referral affiliate, you can set a custom commission here, e.g. %20 or just 20 for flat commission.
translation: Vrednost provizije po meri za doživljenske napotitve - če se transakcija sledi za doživljensko napotenega affiliata, lahko nastavite provizijo po meri tukaj, na primer %20 ali pa le 20 za pavšalno provizijo.

source:
%sThis plugin enables lifetime referrals.%s
Requirements:%s
in order to make it work, you have to pass an identifier which uniquely identifies customer (for example his email)
in the data1 parameter in the sale/lead tracking code.
%s
For example:%s
How it works:
%s
%sIf customer is referred by an affiliate for the first time, the plugin will store the relation between customer (his identifier) and affiliate into the database%s
%sNext time, when the same customer makes a sale (with the same identifier), the application will find the affiliate who originally referred him, and give him commission%s
%sIf no affiliate is found, the process goes normally, so it tries to recognize affiliate from cookie, etc.%s
translation:
%s Ta vtičnik omogoča doživljenske napotitve. %s
Zahteve: %s
da bi zadeva delovala, boste morali prenesti oznako, ki enolično identificira stranko (na primer njegov e-mail)
V data1 parameter v kodi za sledenje prodaje. %s
Na primer: %s
Kako deluje:
%s
%s Če je kupec napoten preko affiliata prvič, bo ta vtičnik shranil odnos med kupcem (njegova oznaka - identifier) in affiliatom v bazo %s
%s Naslednjič, ko bo isti kupec naredil prodajo (z isto oznako), bo aplikacija našla affiliata, ki ga je prvotno napotil in mu dala provizijo %s
%s Če affiliate ni bil najden, bo šel proces normalno naprej, aplikacijo bo poskušala indentificirati affiliata iz piškotka, itd. %s

source: You have to enter a valid API Key so the system can communicate with MailChimp. Get a key at <a target="_parent" href="http://admin.mailchimp.com/account/api">http://admin.mailchimp.com/account/api<a/>
translation: Vnesti morate veljaven ključ API, tako da lahko sistem komunicira z MailChimp. Get ključ na http://admin.mailchimp.com/account/api

source: The secret key will be used to identify a valid data sent from your MailChimp webhook. The key can be any string, e.g. MyPass007
translation: Skrivni ključ se uporablja za identifikacijo veljavnih podatkov, poslane iz vaše MailChimp webhook. Ključ je lahko poljuben niz, na primer MyPass007

source: ID of the list you want an affiliate to be added to (updated in). In case you want to use more lists, separate it with semicolon. How to find my list ID?
translation: ID seznama, v katerega želite dodati affiliata (posodobiti). V primeru, da želite uporabljati več seznamov, jih ločite s podpičji. Kako najti svoj ID seznama?

source: Whether or not a secure connection should be used for communication with MailChimp.
translation: Varao povezava je potrebna za komunikacijo z MailChimp.

source: Whether or not to add new affiliates into your MailChimp list.
translation: O tem, ali dodati nove affiliate v vašo MailChimp seznam ali ne.

source: You have to set all field values! Otherwise the plugin won't work.
translation: Nastaviti morate vse vrednosti polja! Sicer vtičnik ne bo deloval.

source: Please enter a nonempty string into Secret key field. For security reasond, this is required.
translation: Prosimo vnesite neprazen niz v Skrivni ključ. Zaradi varnostnih razlogov, je to potrebno.

source: This plugin creates a new customer (or updates an existing) in a MailChimp list based on affiliate data.
translation: Ta vtičnik ustvari novo stranko (ali posodobi obstoječo) v MailChimp seznam, ki temelji na affiliate podatkih.

source: Use recurring total cost from notification
translation: Uporabite ponavljajoče skupne stroške od obvestila

source: When this is checked, for recurring commission is used total cost from paypal ipn notification insted of total cost from initial payment.
translation: Ko je to onačeno so za ponavljajoče se provizije uporabljeni skupni stroški od PayPal IPN obvestil, namesto celotnih stroškov iz prvega plačila.

source: Whether to use SKU for product IDs or not. By default, product name is set as product ID.
translation: Ali naj se uporabi SKU za ID izdelka ali ne. Za privzeto je ime izdelka določiti kot ID izdelka.

source: If you want to use SKUs then you have to set all field values! Otherwise the plugin won't work.
translation: Če želite uporabiti SKU-je potem boste morali nastaviti vse vrednosti polj! Sicer vtičnik ne bo deloval.

source: Set the custom commission that shall be given to a referring affiliate if he/she happens to be the purchaser.
translation: Nastavite provizijo po meri, ki bo dana napotenemu affiliatu če se zgodi, da sta  on/ona kupec.

source: Choose the transaction Data field in which you are tracking the email address of purchaser/customer
translation: Izberite polje podatkov o transakcijah, v katerih sledite e-poštni naslov kupca / stranke

source: Prohibit Commission If Affiliate Is Purchaser

source: If a sale is referred by an affiliate who is also the purchaser at the same time, then the affiliate gets a custom commission set in this plugin. Don't forget to add email address of purchaser to a transaction data field configured in the plugin.

source: Debugging can be used for troubleshooting. You can choose actions where the system will use INFORMATION log level with debug messages. Otherwise is used general log level for all actions. In production it should be turned off, because it generates multiple history records for each transaction and slows down the system.

Na ta način lahko preverite, kaj skripta počne prav in kaj ji ne uspe. V proizvodnem okolju je treba izključiti ker preveč zapisov zgodovine za vsako transakcijo upočasni sistem.

source: This is a formula based on which all the commissions will be counted. If main commission structure should be set to 1st tier 5%; 2nd tier 4% and 3rd tier 3% the formula would look like %3-%4-%5. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc...
translation: This is a formula based on which all the commissions will be counted. If main commission structure should be set to 1st tier 5%; 2nd tier 4% and 3rd tier 3% the formula would look like %3-%4-%5. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc...

source:
If main commission structure should be set to 1st tier 5%; 2nd tier 4% and 3rd tier 3% the formula would look like %3-%4-%5. In case you want to payout flat commission, the formula requires only numbers: 3-4-5. This structure defines tiers from right to left, meaning the first one from left is top tier, then their child, then grandchild etc... The missing tier commission always goes to the parent affiliate (from right to left).

E.g. in case of five levels %2-%2-%2-%4-%5 the commission structure changes like this, if the last affiliate is missing:
All 5 tiers: %2-%2-%2-%4-%5
4 tiers: %2-%2-%2-%9
3 tiers: %2-%2-%11
2 tiers: %2-%13
1 tier: %15
translation:
Če je glavna struktura provizije 1. stopnje nastavljena 5 %; 2. stopnje 4 % in 3. stopnje 3 % bi bila formula videti kot %3-%4-%5. V primeru, da želite, da izplačilo fiksnih provizij, enačba zahteva samo številke: 3-4-5. Ta struktura določa stopnje od desne proti levi, kar pomeni prvi od leve je na vrhu seznama, potem njegov otrok, nato vnuk itd... Manjkajoče stopnje provizije gredo vedno affiliate staršu (od desne proti levi).

npr. v primeru fiksnih provizij %2-%2-%2-%4-%5 se struktura provizij spremeni tako, če manjka zadnji affiliate:
vseh 5 stopenj: %2-%2-%2-%4-%5
4 stopnja: %2-%2-%2-%9
3 stopnja: %2 %2 %11
2 stopnja: %2 %13
1 stopnja: %15

Vendar v primeru, da obstajajo samo dve stopnji, plačaj ostalih 5 % staršu manjkajočega affiliata. V primeru, da obstaja samo en afiilate, plačajo polnih 15 % provizije affiliatu.

source:
Mandatory: network merchant see it in application and in signup form and have to fill it
Optional: network merchant see it in application and in signup form (can stay empty)

source:
If this option is enabled, the 'custom commission' will be calculated based on residual value of tracked Total Cost less the Maximum Total Cost
example:
'campaign commission' is 30%
'Maximum total cost' is 100
'Commission if over maximum' is 10%
when new sale is created with totalcost $150, commission is computed 30% from $100 + 10% from $50 = $35 (without this checkbox commission is 10% from 150)
translation:
Če je ta možnost omogočena bo provizija po meri izračuna na osnovi preostale vrednosti sledenih skupnih stroškov minus maksimalni skupni stroški
primer:
'Provizija kampanje' je 30%
"Največji celotni strošek" je 100
"Provizija, če je nad maksimumom' je 10%
, ko se ustvari novo prodajo z celotnimi stroški $150, je provizija izračunana 30% od $100 + 10 % od 50 $ = $35 (brez tega potrditvenega polja je provizija 10% od 150)

source:
The last affiliate tier with no parent in a sale will get the commission as a difference between the totalcost and the sum of commissions given to lower tiers.
Notice: Use this plugin only in case you want to pay all the totalcost (100% commission) to your affiliates.
translation:
The last affiliate tier with no parent in a sale will get the commission as a difference between the totalcost and the sum of commissions given to lower tiers.
Notice: Use this plugin only in case you want to pay all the totalcost (100% commission) to your affiliates.

source:
Example 1:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 50%; 2nd tier 30% and 3rd tier 20%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (50%, 30%, 20%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 50% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 50%(lower tiers)
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier) = 100%
Example 2:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 30%; 2nd tier 20% and 3rd tier 10%, for all tiers the commission is 60%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (30%, 20%, 10%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 30% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 30%(lower tiers) = 70%, for all tiers the commission is 100%!
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier), so for all tiers the commission is 100%!
translation:
Example 1:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 50%; 2nd tier 30% and 3rd tier 20%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (50%, 30%, 20%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 50% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 50%(lower tiers)
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier) = 100%
Example 2:
Let's have the main commission structure set like this: 1st tier 30%; 2nd tier 20% and 3rd tier 10%, for all tiers the commission is 60%. Now here are some cases:
  • Commission for all 3 tiers: Every tier gets the commission noramlly (30%, 20%, 10%)
  • Commission for 2 tiers: The 1st tier gets 30% and the 2nd tier gets 'totalcost' - 30%(lower tiers) = 70%, for all tiers the commission is 100%!
  • Commission for 1 tier: The 1st tier gets commission of 'totalcost' - 0(there is no lower tier), so for all tiers the commission is 100%!

source:
When you have configured your campaigns, defined correct commissions, and created some banners/links, you should test the system.
The best is to simulate the whole process from affiliate’s and your point of view:
  1. Sign up as some testing affiliate – after approval you should receive confirmation email with your password, and you should be able to log in to your affiliate panel
  2. Log in to affiliates panel, get the code for banners/links and put them onto some testing page
  3. Click on the banner and check that the click is registered
  4. After the click, try to make test sale and check that sale commission was registered in affiliate system (only for per sale or per lead commissions)
If you experience some problems in any of these steps, turn on Debug event logging and look at Troubleshooting%s
translation:
When you have configured your campaigns, defined correct commissions, and created some banners/links, you should test the system.
The best is to simulate the whole process from affiliate’s and your point of view:
  1. Sign up as some testing affiliate – after approval you should receive confirmation email with your password, and you should be able to log in to your affiliate panel
  2. Log in to affiliates panel, get the code for banners/links and put them onto some testing page
  3. Click on the banner and check that the click is registered
  4. After the click, try to make test sale and check that sale commission was registered in affiliate system (only for per sale or per lead commissions)
If you experience some problems in any of these steps, turn on Debug event logging and look at Troubleshooting%s
